		<h2>Tripping is getting out of the routine.</h2>
	</div>
	<p>It is going out and exploring the world. Looking for the next shot is not more than an excuse to go to places that otherwise would have been missed, whether it's a country or a dark alley. It makes wonder what's behind a closed door, after a turn in the road going to the wrong direction. Photography gives meaning to this curiosity and Tripping is a place to share it.</p>
